INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS
=========================



PREREQUISITES
-------------

- OMNeT++ (5.0 - 5.1.1)


FEATURES

PostgreSQL:
- Requires libpqxx

SQLite:
- Requires sqlite3 lib

PCAPNG:
- Requires inet framework
- Check inet framework under project [Preferences -> Project References]


UBUNTU

SQLite:
- Install SQLite3: apt install sqlite3 libsqlite3-dev


WINDOWS

SQLite:
- Download SQLite3 binaries for Windows
- In the mingwenv export PATH=$PATH:<path to folder containing sqlite3.dll>
- Start OMNeT++ from mingwenv
- In OMNeT++ in project [Preferences -> C++ General -> Paths and Symbols -> Library Paths] add <path to folder containing sqlite3.dll>